           IF CLAVE-1-CAP NOT = 0 GO TO SIGA-INI.
           PERFORM CLAVE-SYS.
           PERFORM BORRA-CLAVE.
       SIGA-INI.
           PERFORM TIT-PAN.
           PERFORM TITU-PAN.
           PERFORM FECHA-PAN.
           PERFORM OPC-MODA.
           PERFORM MEN-MODA-A.
           MOVE 3 TO SW3.
       CARGO-MOD.
           ACCEPT COD1 LINE TAB-LIN(SW3) POSITION TAB-COL(SW3)
                   ON EXCEPTION EXCEP GO TO TAREAS.
           GO TO CARGO-MOD.
