                    STOP RUN.
           IF F01 GO TO ACTU.
           IF F05 MOVE 0 TO REP GO TO LIST-NUM.
           IF F06 MOVE 9 TO REP GO TO LIST-NUM.
           IF F07 GO TO LIST-LIN.
           IF F08 GO TO LIST-PEN.
           GO TO CARGO-MOD.
