           MOVE "DIGITE <F9> MOD" TO MEN-1.
           MOVE "IFICA STOCK    " TO MEN-2.
           MOVE "               " TO MEN-3.
           PERFORM MENS-PAN.
           MOVE 3 TO SW3.
           PERFORM CAP-COD1.
           MOVE SPACES TO MEN-1 MEN-2 MEN-3.
           PERFORM MENS-PAN.
           IF ESCAP 
      ****15/5/95                     PERFORM PIE-P-1 
                           CLOSE IMP01 
                           UNLOCK ART02 RECORD
                           PERFORM CIERRA-A GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF F09 GO TO MODI.
           UNLOCK ART02 RECORD
           GO TO CARGA-COD.
