           PERFORM MEN-MODA-S.
           MOVE 1 TO SW3.
           MOVE "LIST.STOCK P/LINEAS" TO D20-CAP.
           PERFORM MODA-PAN.
           PERFORM PANTA-LIN.
           PERFORM CARGO-EMP THRU CARGO-EMP-F.
